{"tid":1977888,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃食店應考慮司法覆核政府濫用食肆抗疫規例","createTime":"2020-04-18T09:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T12:01:26.000Z","uid":70786,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"85b90c3d35d4556227662a69a2506a6371f52909","tid":1977888,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:49:29.000Z","msg":"第599F章 《預防及控制疾病(規定及指示)(業務及處所)規例》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599F?xpid=ID_1585303941495_002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap599F%3Fxpid%3DID_1585303941495_002&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeojsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=efcc04ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599F?xpid=ID_1585303941495_002</a><br />\n<br />\n8.局長就表列處所發指示<br />\n(1)為預防、抵禦、阻延或以其他方式控制指明疾病的個案或傳播，局長可發出指示，在該指示所指明的期間，就任何或所有以下事宜，施加規定或限制 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)在任何表列處所經營的任何業務(或進行的任何活動)的運作模式；<br />\n(b)關閉任何表列處所(或任何表列處所的部分範圍)；<br />\n(c)任何表列處所在一日之中的營業時段。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(2)任何根據第(1)款發出的指示所指明的期間，均不得超過14日。</span><br />\n<br />\n食肆抗疫規例由三月尾開始，已經超過十四日<br />\n政府之前延長措施至4月23日<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.以上情況政府有冇違憲？措施同強制徵用食肆一半坐位一樣，應否向受影響食肆補償？<br />\n2.黑警踩場導致黃店捐失營業額，係咪可以索償？<br />\n<br />\n黃店生意好，可能有人睇唔過眼，整D規例出嚟，藍店不嬲都冇客佢地冇所謂，但黃藍店就一樣收定額資助，有咩理由唔係根據營業額去計算抗疫資肋，咁樣政府係咪干預緊自由市場？<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊第二輪資助好似係根據面積去計算抗疫資助添，D藍店例如屢違法例嘅燉炳強就發發，咁多間分店數資助都數到手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd87060905374aac9b1b8a25b76e612b218ae2a2","tid":1977888,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"林鄭個政府不嬲都係頭痛醫頭<br />\n食肆都未爆群組居然又會咁上心走去搞食肆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e820f3ef2ae84fd9a0f878146baaf23061a1e8","tid":1977888,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"真係想知香港成千個案有咩證據證明食肆高危<br />\n林鄭同行會訂呢D規例有冇根據科學?<br />\n定係好似佢所講同限聚令一樣其實係冇科學根據?"},{"pid":"fda1b608700f0e5f44373f4c037d410944b068e2","tid":1977888,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"搞到人地營業額受捐失<br />\n政府俾錢唔應該叫資助而係叫賠償"},{"pid":"6257b60b70e4a3bed72bc13714c01b031dd37a56","tid":1977888,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"支持受影響食店組成聯盟入稟告香港政府亂鳩咁嚟<br />\n導致生意額受損<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ae57fd1803291d2cc40b80c81227872646bb21","tid":1977888,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"冇話只可以發出指示一次，只係話每次最長14日，其實佢發過2次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202416e/cgn2020241616.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202416e%2Fcgn2020241616.pdf&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeojsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=d9aa8dc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202416e/cgn2020241616.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202422e/cgn2020242225.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202422e%2Fcgn2020242225.pdf&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeojsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=1d65bbe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202422e/cgn2020242225.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"de3337ee67adea68d257093538402726f47a8675","tid":1977888,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"90ae57fd1803291d2cc40b80c81227872646bb21","tid":1977888,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"冇話只可以發出指示一次，只係話每次最長14日，其實佢發過2次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202416e/cgn2020241616.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202416e%2Fcgn2020241616.pdf&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeojsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=d9aa8dc8\" target=\"